### 1、需求

快速入门，设计一个最简单购物流程， **开始==》加入购物车==》付款 》物流发货》结束**。  
假设这是一个大型异构分布式系统，加入购物车，物流发货是java系统，付款是nodejs系统。

### 三、搭建业务系统

创建一个maven工程，填写工程名，及maven GAV信息。

添加类，分别订阅流程中的加入购物车任务和物流发货任务。  
com.shopping.subscribe.SubscribeTask

```
package com.shopping.subscribe;

import lombok.extern.slf4j.Slf4j;
import org.camunda.bpm.client.ExternalTaskClient;
import org.camunda.bpm.engine.variable.Variables;
import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;

import javax.annotation.PostConstruct;
import java.util.Map;

@Component
@Slf4j
public class SubscribeTask {
    //引擎端url 前缀
    private final static String CAMUNDA_BASE_URL = "http://47.100.121.32:8080/engine-rest";

    private ExternalTaskClient client = null;

    private ExternalTaskClient getClient() {
        if (client == null) {
            client = ExternalTaskClient.create()
                    .baseUrl(CAMUNDA_BASE_URL)
                    .asyncResponseTimeout(10000) // long polling timeout
                    .build();
        }
        return client;
    }


    @PostConstruct
    public void handleShoppingCart() {
        getClient().subscribe("shopping_cart")
                .processDefinitionKey("Process_0zhcpaj")
                .lockDuration(2000)
                .handler((externalTask, externalTaskService) -> {
                    log.info("订阅到加入购物车任务");
                    Map<String, Object> goodVariable = Variables.createVariables()
                            .putValue("size", "xl")
                            .putValue("count", 2);

                    externalTaskService.complete(externalTask, goodVariable);
                }).open();
    }

    @PostConstruct
    public void handleLogisticsDelivery() {
        getClient().subscribe("logistics_delivery")
                .processDefinitionKey("Process_0zhcpaj")
                .lockDuration(2000)
                .handler((externalTask, externalTaskService) -> {
                    Object toWhere = externalTask.getVariable("toWhere");
                    log.info("收到发货任务，目的地：{}", String.valueOf(toWhere));

                    externalTaskService.complete(externalTask);
                }).open();
    }

}

```

#### 搭建NodeJs工程

前提：安装Node10以上环境，适当的开发工具，推荐vscode  
参考：[https://blog.csdn.net/qq\_35457469/article/details/123302851](https://blog.csdn.net/qq_35457469/article/details/123302851)

创建工程，依次执行以下命令：

```
mkdir shopping-service-nodejs
cd shopping-service-nodejs
npm init -y
```

安装[camunda](https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=camunda&spm=1001.2101.3001.7020)\-external-task-client-js

```
npm install camunda-external-task-client-js
npm install -D open
```

![在这里插入图片描述](data:image/png;base64,)

vscode 打shopping-service-nodejs 工程，添加subscribe.js订阅处理付款任务。

```
const { Client, logger ,Variables} = require('camunda-external-task-client-js');
const open = require('open');

// configuration for the Client:
//  - 'baseUrl': url to the Process Engine
//  - 'logger': utility to automatically log important events
//  - 'asyncResponseTimeout': long polling timeout (then a new request will be issued)
const config = { baseUrl: 'http://47.100.121.32:8080/engine-rest', use: logger, asyncResponseTimeout: 10000 };


const client = new Client(config);

// 订阅BPMN中付款 topic: 'pay'，processDefinitionKey可以指定是哪个流程，可能其他流程也是相同topic
client.subscribe('pay', { processDefinitionKey: "Process_0zhcpaj" },
    async function ({ task, taskService }) {

        // Put your business logic here

        // Get a process variable
        const size = task.variables.get('size');
        const count = task.variables.get('count');

        console.log(`顾客下单尺寸： ${size} 数量：'${count}'...`);

        const processVariables = new Variables()
            .set("toWhere", "shanghai China");

        // Complete the task
        try {
            await taskService.complete(task,processVariables);
            console.log('I completed my task successfully!!');
        } catch (e) {
            console.error(`Failed completing my task, ${e}`);
        }
    });

```
